OL,5,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FA retired secretary has to visit
OL,7,     Fher tenant in prison in order to
OL,8,     Fretake possession of her
OL,9,     Fbuy-to-let flat.
OL,10,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,11,     FWith over 120,000 cars stolen in
OL,12,     Fthe UK every year, Traffic Cops
OL,13,     Fare cracking down on car crime. In
OL,14,     Fthis episode, officers are
OL,15,     Fstretched to the limit with three
OL,16,     Fpursuits in 30 minutes.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
