OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FPolice endeavours to tackle drunk
OL,7,     For drug drivers. Police control
OL,8,     Freceives reports of suspected drug
OL,9,     Fdriver. After the driver fails to
OL,10,     Fstop, cops are forced into a
OL,11,     Fhigh-speed pursuit.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FWith almost a fifth of fatal
OL,14,     Finjuries on UK's roads caused by
OL,15,     Fdrink driving, cops face pressure
OL,16,     Fto stop drivers under the
OL,17,     Finfluence. A biker is knocked off
OL,18,     Fhis bike by a drink driver.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
