OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Emma McMullen has her work cut
OL,7,     Fout trying to help a patient with
OL,8,     Fa challenging condition - and ends
OL,9,     Fup needing a wipe down! And a
OL,10,     Fpatient's mole makes it hard to
OL,11,     Fbrush her hair.
OL,12,G0000 Scam City: Don't Get Caught Out!
OL,13,     FNew Delhi is one of the world's
OL,14,     Fgreatest historical cities but
OL,15,     FConor Woodman discovers a world of
OL,16,     Fhustlers, conmen and scammers all
OL,17,     Fdoing their best to relieve
OL,18,     Ftourists of their cash.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
